prismic-embed/field.description: The Prismic embed field to render.

prismic-embed/wrapper.description: An HTML tag name, a component, or a functional component used to wrap the output. Defaults to `"div"`.

prismic-image/field.description: The Prismic image field to render.

prismic-link/field.description: The Prismic link field or document to render.

prismic-link/link-resolver.description: A link resolver function used to resolve links when not using the route resolver parameter with `@prismicio/client`. Defaults to the link resolver provided to `@prismicio/vue` plugin if configured.

prismic-link/target.description: An explicit `target` attribute to apply to the rendered link.

prismic-link/rel.description: An explicit `rel` attribute to apply to the rendered link.

prismic-link/blank-target-rel-attribute.description: Value of the `rel` attribute to use on links rendered with `target="_blank"`. Defaults to the one provided to `@prismicio/vue` plugin if configured, `"noopener noreferrer"` otherwise.

prismic-rich-text/field.description: The Prismic rich text or title field to render.

prismic-rich-text/link-resolver.description: A link resolver function used to resolve links when not using the route resolver parameter with `@prismicio/client`. Defaults to the link resolver provided to `@prismicio/vue` plugin if configured.

prismic-rich-text/html-serializer.description: An HTML serializer to customize the way rich text fields are rendered. Defaults to the HTML serializer provided to `@prismicio/vue` plugin if configured.

prismic-rich-text/wrapper.description: An HTML tag name, a component, or a functional component used to wrap the output. Defaults to `"div"`.

prismic-text/field.description: The Prismic rich text or title field to render.

prismic-text/separator.description: Separator used to join each element. Defaults to `" "` (a space)

prismic-text/wrapper.description: An HTML tag name, a component, or a functional component used to wrap the output. Defaults to `"div"`.

slice-zone/slices.description: List of Slice data from the Slice Zone.

slice-zone/components.description: A record mapping Slice types to Vue components.

slice-zone/context.description: Arbitrary data made available to all Slice components.

slice-zone/default-component.description: A component or a functional component rendered if a component mapping from the `components` prop cannot be found. Defaults to the Slice Zone default component provided to `@prismicio/vue` plugin if configured, otherwise `null` when `process.env.NODE_ENV === "production"` else `"todo-slice-component"`

slice-zone/wrapper.description: An HTML tag name, a component, or a functional component used to wrap the output. Defaults to `"div"`.
